name: The Queen's Dreams: Rise of the Phoenix
description:
The day after yesterday brought a new found hope.
A chance to thaw the frost from the eyelids of war.
The glaciers broke down and the flames fell loosely through the waters.
This would be a new age.
This was the beginning of a fresh start.
The air was crisp.
The amber glow soothing.
The belief in hell dissipated.
The karma and joy of these feelings reassured that everything from here was good.
